---
metadata: {
    partial_name: 'Website | Layout | Placeholder image'
}
---


{%- comment -%}
Placeholder for image content
- handly code block to use if there's no images yet provided for the projet
- accepts variable 'size' to control the padding [medium, large]
- ie. {%- include 'modules/website/content/placeholder_image', size: 'large' -%}
Note: This is use in addon template like Ecommerce
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="placeholder-img vertical-align-middle">
  <div>
    {%- if size == 'large' and size != 'medium' -%}
      <div class="spacer section"></div>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if size == 'large' or size == 'medium' -%}
      <div class="spacer x-large"></div>
    {%- endif -%}
    {% comment %} placeholder: icon-panorame {% endcomment %}
    <i class="icon-panorame"></i>
    {%- if size == 'large' or size == 'medium' -%}
      <div class="spacer x-large"></div>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if size == 'large' and size != 'medium' -%}
      <div class="spacer section"></div>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</div>